this one I'm currently in."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0y6uotzniqd4_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 13:34 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 3\n• cron:ed2d0b5d (5p QLHV): running — 5-min progress monitoring (QLHV ecosystem) — ~3h 3m\n• cron:6f3323ef (5p DTLX): running — 5-min progress monitoring (DTLX ecosystem) — ~9h 9m\n• cron:e7885813 (Agent Status): running — Heartbeat monitor to Lead — ~2m\n\nPipeline: HEARTBEAT_OK ✅\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• No blockers. All critical monitors operational.\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":8372,"output":916,"totalTokens":23465,"cacheRead":13849,"cacheWrite":328,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776173660736,"responseId":"062d755d8ba9a12800a405f18119250a","__openclaw":{"id":"ee418edf","seq":4}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The session_send timed out. This means the target session is waiting for something. Let me check the session to see if it's still alive or if it's in a state that doesn't accept messages.\n\nActually, looking at the target session (telegram:direct:6053576134), it has status \"done\" and endedAt: 1776162158012. That session has ended. The delivery context was set to \"telegram:direct:6053576134\" but the session is done.\n\nHowever, since it's the direct session to Lead's Telegram, perhaps OpenClaw will still route the message to the Telegram channel even if the session is done. But the tool timed out.\n \nThe timeout likely occurred because the session is in a done state, so it can't process the message synchronously. The previous successful send at 13:24 UTC shows the delivery mechanism should work, but this session needs time to initialize and isn't immediately responsive.\n\nLooking at the session status