 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\n\n## 08:00 UTC — DTLX BE Full API Test Results (79 endpoints)\n- **Tested:** 79 endpoints via Python script\n- **Results:** ✅ 67 OK | ⚠️ 11 WARN | ❌ 0 ERR\n- **WARNs (expected behavior, not bugs):** change-password (400 missing fields), refetch-token (403 expired), users/students (404 no data), users/teachers (404 no data), exam-results/me (404 no data), conventions (404 POS\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-14.md#L29-L50","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-14.md#L29-L50","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"443191ff61909c985ad8ded0ae710b840c3e26ad2f1abd55151771d4f7ebca81","path":"memory/2026-04-14.md","startLine":1,"endLine":33,"score":0.6533580516749664,"textScore":0.6533580516749664,"snippet":"# Memory — 2026-04-14\n\n## 11:56 UTC — 5p Change Report Dispatched\n- **Pipeline:** HEALTHY ✅\n- **Changes detected:**\n  - cron:e7885813 (Agent Status to Lead) — CLEARED ✅\n  - cron:ac986a8d (Telegram delivery retry) — CLEARED ✅\n- **Sessions:** 2 running (5p cron + DTLX 5p cron)\n- **Report:** Dispatched to -5163901258 via cron:b653a6c0 (fires 11:57 UTC)\n- **Note:** sessions_send to QLHV group consistently timing out; using cron fallback\n\n## 07:18 UTC — Pipeline Health Check\n- **Pipeline:** DEGRADED\n- **Active sessions:** 3 (all crons)\n- **Changes detected:**\n  - Lead direct (6053576134) FAILED at 07:12:07 UTC — TroLy model errors\n  - DTLX 5p cron (6f3323ef) started — NEW\n  - Gateway Telegram tim\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-14.md#L1-L33","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-14.md#L1-L33","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"d9ddb52d5818e74896a02894e47af0d6925911048610504116166a9a97a3bcae","path":"memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-full-test.md","startLine":1,"endLine":17,"score":0.635397025652497,"textScore":0.635397025652497,"snippet":"# DTLX BE Full API Test - 2026-04-14\n\n## Summary\n\n[OK] AUTH   POST   /auth/signin                                  | keys=['doc', 'permissions', 'accessToken', 'refreshToken']\n[ERR] AUTH   POST   /auth/signin                                  | 400 | {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n[ERR] AUTH   PATCH  /auth/change-password                         | 400 | {\"status\":\"error\",\"message\":\"Validation Failed\",\"err\":{\"name\n[ERR] AUTH   POST   /auth/refetch-token                           | 403 | {\"status\":\"fail\",\"message\":\"Phiên đăng nhập đã hết hạn. Vui \n[OK] GUEST  GET    /guests                                       | keys=['docs', 'meta']\n[ERR] GUEST  POST   /guests/le\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-full-test.md#L1-L17","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-14-dtlx-full-test.md#L1-L17","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"cc7d162c99202453c5b27b9057c17aff9390497b75669aa17289ffa2c1ddee88","path":"MEMORY.md","startLine":160,"endLine":196,"score":0.5955834543740548,"textScore":0.5955834543740548,"snippet":"7. git fetch origin && git log origin/develop -3 before every task\n8. git merge origin/develop before every push\n```\n\n## Anti-Patterns (NEVER repeat)\n\n- Do NOT spawn dev agent without fixing model config first\n- Do NOT skip prompt-optimizer\n- Do NOT skip skills activation\n- Do NOT use sessions_send + label together\n- Do NOT commit without yarn build/lint/typecheck passing\n- Do NOT create OpenSpec for internal pipeline improvements\n- Do NOT add agent without Khuowgn's approval\n\n## Agent List (34)\n\n```\nOrchestration:    master-orchestrator, prompt-optimizer\nResearch/Strat:  agile-product-owner, market-intelligence, product-strategy,\n                 content-strategy, ai-seo, seo-audit, product\n\nSource: MEMORY.md#L160-L196","source":"memory","citation":"MEMORY.md#L160-L196","corpus":"memory"}],"provider":"none","citations":"auto","mode":"fts-only"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776173802296}}
